"append:choice[1]/text"
msgstr "Ask Leah about this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:10
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[2]/text"
msgstr "Ask TRACKER about this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:14
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[3]/text"
msgstr "Ask the Flagship about this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:18
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[4]/text"
msgstr "Ask the Trash Eater about this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:22
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//mod:findName[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW\"]/mod-"
"append:choice[5]/text"
msgstr "Ask the The Architect about this."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:28
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_LEAH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We've been through a lot together, haven't we?\" Leah turns away from you "
"and looks out at the wreckage of the flagship. \"I don't think Wither has "
"the right idea. Sure, multiverse drives are dangerous, but look at us! Think"
" of how many amazing movie-like rivalries we'll be ruining if we detonate "
"that bomb! If we exist then there's plenty more out there.\" Leah pauses "
"before turning back to you, \"Out of all the infinite rivalries in the "
"universe, this one is special, you're not just any old bitch, you're MY "
"beyatch.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:31
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_LEAH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:37
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_FLAGSHIP\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"As soon as the words escape you, you immediately wonder why you just asked "
"the ship, an innanimate object, about this all-powerful device. Just as "
"you're about to leave the helm, the comms blink to life, an unintelligible "
"garble of noise erupting from it. Shortly thereafter, it stops, notifying "
"you that \"you\" have just uploaded blueprints for a Cruiser. You'll never "
"know what it might be, should you detonate the Paragon."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:40
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_FLAGSHIP\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:46
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_TRACKER\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"We did it.\" says Tracker, seemingly extremely content. \"The Protogen "
"Project has kicked the Rebellion's royally blasted behind big-time - and it "
"was about time we did. Let's go get a good look at the wreckage. I want to "
"take as many trophies as we can fit in the hold.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:48
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_TRACKER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:54
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_TRASH\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"THIS IS NOT THE END... THIS IS NOT THE END... SOMETHING GREATER LURKS IN "
"THE SHADOWS...\" the Trash Eater seems shaken. But what could possibly be "
"worse than this?"

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:57
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_TRASH\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:63
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_ZOG\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"\"In our victory here, I see that my creations have serviced both you and "
"myself wonderfully. May your next act, whatever it may be, act as the "
"capstone to my magnum opus.\""

#: src-en/data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append:67
msgid ""
"data/events_sector_showdown.xml.append$//event[@name=\"TRUE_VICTORY_CREW_ZOG\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "Continue..."
